    <item>
      <title>Updated biograpies available</title>
      <link>https://ric-unknownartist.projektemacher.org/post/updated-biography/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 21:44:57 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://ric-unknownartist.projektemacher.org/post/updated-biography/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;After it turned out that Fritz Neumann (1928-2014) &lt;a href=&#34;https://ric-unknownartist.projektemacher.org/post/mystery-again/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;is not Ric&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;, Mark Strong has updated the biographies at &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.meibohmfinearts.com/artists/details/2873&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Meibohm Fine Arts&lt;/a&gt;&#xA; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.askart.com/artist/Fritz_Neumann/11057559/Fritz_Neumann.aspx&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;AskArt.com&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Many thanks to Mark for this!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Hopefully the false attributions on eBay and other auction sites will now be less&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
